    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个患者预约系统的时序图，核心流程是用户通过SchedulerApp添加事件，然后系统要自动关联到HealthTech_LabAnalyzer这个设备，同时触发HIPAA合规的数据存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，HealthTech_LabAnalyzer是事件的业务来源对吧？那Event对象创建之后，是通过EventDAO写入HIPAA_Vault，还是直接由Event自己处理持久化？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "通过EventDAO来解耦，Event只负责领域逻辑，持久化交给EventDAO，并且明确标注使用HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault作为存储后端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出用户请求添加事件到SchedulerApp，然后SchedulerApp创建Event并传入LabAnalyzer参数，接着Event调用EventDAO的add_event方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "add_event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有提醒功能，用户添加事件后可以设置提醒，这里需要Reminder和ReminderService两个参与者，提醒的触发源也是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reminder",
        "ReminderService",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
